      "writtenOn": "2019-11-05T22:48:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "we don\u0027t really know that here. for example, we may decide to shutdown the server if a receive garbage over TCP from a subprocess and that is not an internal server error.\n\nalso, this means errors in errC and returned by Run() are inconsistent. I think we should just return the err as is",
